src_text: Modlolo wa Nhluvukiso lowu Simekiweke eka Swifundzatsongo
trg_text: District Based Development Model

src_text: Khabinete yi amukela nsimeko wa ximfumo hi Phuresidente Cyril Ramaphosa, wa Modlolo wa Nhluvukiso lowu Simekiweke eka Swifundzatsongo eka Masipala wa Xifundzatsongo xa OR Tambo, eKapa-Vuhumadyamb Modlolo lowu wu tisa endhawini yin we swiyenge swinharhu swa mfumo ku pfunetana, tirhisana na ku katsanisa ntirho wa swona ku ri na nkongomiso wo hlawuleka eka xifundzatsongo lexi ku ololoxa mitlhontlho ya nhluvukiso na ku kondletela mphakelo wa vukorhokeri, maxavelo ya tinhundzu na vukorhokeri swa le ndhawini leyi na ku tumbuluxiwa ka mitirh Modlolo lowu wu amukeriwile hi Khabinete, mitlawa ya mfumo wa miganga, valawuri va ndhavuko na Khansele yo Tirhisana ya Phuresidente (PCC).
trg_text: Cabinet welcomes the official launch by President Cyril Ramaphosa, of the new District Based Development Model in the OR Tambo District Municipality, in the Eastern Cap The model brings together the three spheres of government to collaborate, cooperate and integrate their work with special reference to the district to address developmental challenges and promote service delivery, localised procurement and job creatio This model was endorsed by Cabinet, local government structures, traditional authorities and the President s Coordinating Council (PCC).

src_text: Tanihileswi Xifundzatsongo xa OR Tambo a xi ri xona xo sungula ku simeka ximfumo modlolo lowu, wu ta simekiwa eka 44 wa swifundzatsongo hinkwaswo na 8 wa madorobakulu etikweni hinkwar Swi tisa mfumo ekusuhi na vanhu hi ku katsa vaakatiko na vakhomaxiave eka nhluvukiso wa kungu rin we na mphakelo vukorhokeri byo hambanahambana na ku tumbuluxa swivandlanene swa ikhonomi eka levhele ya xifundzatsongo ya masungul
trg_text: Whilst OR Tambo District was the first to officially launch this model, it will be rolled-out to all 44 districts and 8 metros across the countr
